                                <h2>Our minimum 3-week vacation policy</h2>
                                <p>
                                    Over the years we&#x27;ve evolved our
                                    approach to vacation and time off. We
                                    currently have a minimum 3-week vacation
                                    policy to encourage teammates to recharge
                                    away from work.
                                </p>
